35
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,640
Stay away from Lin Yiyuan.

36
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,280
Why?

37
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,680
I have my reasons.

38
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,400
