40
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,280
What story are you going to make up this time?

41
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,000
Then take a guess.

42
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,840
Who will be the next to die?

43
00:04:58,880 --> 00:04:59,960
I'm not in the mood.

44
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,520
Go back.

45
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,440
Do you not want to know, or are you afraid to know?

46
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:07,160
What is there for me to be afraid of?

47
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,120
What am I afraid of?

48
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,840
I know you killed those people.

49
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,560
Otherwise, you wouldn't know everything.

50
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,560
Since you did it,

51
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,440
