52
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,360
Before you came,

53
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,360
when I was with Mom,

54
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,840
I was always fine.

55
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:29,000
She protected you, the devil, from beginning to end.

56
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,120
