00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:14,960
Niannian.

64
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:16,160
Happy birthday.

65
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,120
Are you cold?

66
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,680
Are you happy?

67
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:27,880
I'm happy.

68
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,280
Good girl.

69
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:47,080
Come on, let's cut the cake.

