You all come and cut it together.

72
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,640
Sorry.

73
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,520
Attorney Lin

74
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,960
I’ve already found

75
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,760
a way to reduce Li Xiulan’s sentence.

76
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:44,920
It’s not about reducing the sentence.

77
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:46,560
It’s about proving her innocence.

78
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,800
My mom is completely innocent.

79
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,680
What are you talking about?

80
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,560
There’s something I’ve never told anyone.

81
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:04,320
But I have to tell you now.

82
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:07,680
I suspect she’s the one who committed the murder.

83
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:09,120
Who?

84
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:10,880
My sister.

85
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:12,320
No.

86
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,800
To be precise, I don’t even know who she is.

87
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,000
She suddenly showed up at my house.

88
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,120
And then

89
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,120
everything started to change.

90
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:25,000
She knows everything—it must be her.

91
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,240
She must be the one who killed.

92
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,880
Otherwise, she wouldn’t have known in advance.

93
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,880
And then she pinned everything on my mom.

94
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,680
I don’t know why my mom is taking the blame for her.

95
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,560
My mom said she’s a liar.

96
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,680
She’s not my sister.

97
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,560
So, Attorney Lin, you have to help me.

98
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,040
Help me investigate her.

99
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:47,040
Help me find evidence that Li Meng committed the murder.

100
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,360
I want to tell all this to the police.

101
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:54,040
You said this person’s name is Li Meng, right?

102
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,560
Yes.

103
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,000
Then I think

104
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,920
it’s better if you don’t tell the police just yet.

105
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,800
To avoid making things more complicated.

106
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,880
How about this—

107
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:13,120
Calm down for now.

108
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,240
Tomorrow, I can help you

109
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,560
look into this person named

110
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,120
Li Meng.

111
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:20,920
Li Meng.

112
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,040
Captain Qin

113
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,560
Didn't Bai Fan already mention

114
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,680
one possible motive for Li Xiulan's murder?

115
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,680
Why are you...

116
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,560
Li Xiulan has already confessed to killing your son

117
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,480
and even admitted to trying to kill you.

118
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:57,800
Why are you so eager to see me?

119
00:10:58,680 --> 00:10:59,680
What do you want to tell me?

120
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:02,880
Why did my son have to die like that?

121
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,680
Li Xiulan and her daughter

122
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,480
are both worthless.

123
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:12,480
They're lowly, and they still want to harm me.

124
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:16,560
Ms. Bai, please calm down.

125
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,000
Tell us what Li Xiulan did to you.

126
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,040
Explain everything clearly to us.

127
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:23,800
She tried to kill me.

128
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,680
She wanted to kill everyone.

129
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:30,000
She knocked me out.

130
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,880
Then she threatened me.

131
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:35,680
She told me not to reveal that secret.

132
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,680
Luckily, I survived.

133
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:42,560
Otherwise, you wouldn't be seeing me now.

134
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,240
What secret?

135
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:52,560
Rape

136
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,680
Zhang Xiaochuan

137
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,920
Once raped her daughter

138
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,800
Isn't that clear enough?

139
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,160
She's taking revenge for her daughter

140
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:14,120
Then what was her motive for killing Bai Tao?

141
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,680
Did Bai Tao participate in the rape?

142
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:17,240
No

143
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,240
My son didn't participate

144
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:21,040
He was forced

145
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,680
My son is very well-behaved

146
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,480
He's so timid

147
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,560
Bai Tao is obedient

148
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,120
He did threaten Li Xiulan

149
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,800
And he blackmailed her

150
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,360
We have evidence for all of this

151
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,360
When it comes to your son

152
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,480
You just deny his involvement

153
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,160
Shut up

154
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,360
Say less

155
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,240
Okay

156
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,680
The record of this rape case

157
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,120
We will investigate

158
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:53,720
Criminal record

159
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,040
There isn't a single trace.

160
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:58,800
No trace at all.

161
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:02,040
Li Xiulan chose to endure it herself.

162
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:04,040
No one forced her.

163
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:07,440
Officer Qin

164
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,440
You can try.

165
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:12,040
See if you can find anything.

166
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:13,800
Are you saying

167
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:17,120
this matter was covered up, right?

168
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,440
My son is dead.

169
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,440
None of them should expect to get away with it.

170
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:25,840
I'm the only one left who knows.

171
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:31,000
Do you still remember the exact time and place?

172
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,200
Of course.

173
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:40,080
I'll never forget that day.

174
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,960
1998

175
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:50,520
In the fields outside the Shigang County Gas Plant

176
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:54,840
Officer Qin

177
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:58,520
How old were you that year?

178
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,000
Twenty-one.

179
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,640
It was from that year on

180
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,760
that everything changed.

181
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,200
Help!

182
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:34,520
Help!

183
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,000
Help!

184
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:39,640
Mom.

185
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,760
