186
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,000
Quick, close the window.

187
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,400
It's raining too hard.

188
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,080
No, the rain is coming in.

189
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,080
I really hear someone crying.

190
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,960
Close the window.

191
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,640
There's no one out there.

192
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:52,880
I'll go down and take a look.

193
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,200
Sit down quickly.

194
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,960
It's so dark today.

195
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,080
You misheard.

196
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:59,520
Young man, sit properly.

197
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,760
The bus is about to start.

198
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:01,120
Sit.

199
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,440
I don't even know

200
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:15,640
if it's fate or something else.

201
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,440
There was a heavy rain.

202
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:24,000
I really heard someone crying.

203
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:34,760
The rape case from back then.

204
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,520
That was your motive for murder, right?

205
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:42,000
What did my daughter do wrong?

206
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,320
Why did they do this to her?

207
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:48,840
They deserve to die.

208
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:51,320
Bai Tao, Zhang Xiaochuan.

209
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:53,000
